c bias against the AAE errors: across three different qualities, essays containing AAE errors are more likely to fail the test than their counterparts do. On the other hand, raters were not as critical of ESL errors as SAE errors. %0a%3c %0a%3c Source: %0a%3c https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S107529351100047X%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
